+.TH "SHADOWCONFIG" 8 "19 Apr 1997" "" ""
+.SH NAME
+shadowconfig \- toggle shadow passwords on and off
+.SH "SYNOPSIS"
+.ad l
+.hy 0
+.HP 13
+\fBshadowconfig\fR \fB\fIon\fR\fR | \fB\fIoff\fR\fR
